# a5ca2325f40c4a9db9f6668a75be5d7b
#: ../../controlpanel.rst:1212
#: ../../controlpanel.rst:1208
msgid "If you click the \"Add\" button, a pop-up menu will prompt you for the name of the new group. Once you press \"OK\", the group will be added to the \"Groups\" column."
