# 74feba93daf84a54b61bd6758a8d0e31
#: ../../controlpanel.rst:1215
#: ../../controlpanel.rst:1211
msgid "If you click the \"Remove\" button, the highlighted group will automatically be deleted after you press the \"Apply\" button, so be sure to do this with care. Again, do **not** remove any groups that you did not create yourself or applications that used to work may stop working."
